UP SKY

1:15:05.041 --> 1:15:06.791
UP SKY

1:15:06.875 --> 1:15:07.791
We're not moving.

1:15:14.708 --> 1:15:16.916
Are you the Monkey King?

1:15:17.000 --> 1:15:18.208
Changing forms every day?

1:15:29.833 --> 1:15:30.666
Thank you.

1:15:31.250 --> 1:15:32.416
Thank you.

1:15:33.916 --> 1:15:35.083
Hello?

1:15:35.708 --> 1:15:36.875
Curly,

1:15:36.958 --> 1:15:37.875
it's me,

1:15:37.958 --> 1:15:38.875
San.

1:15:38.958 --> 1:15:40.125
So this is the situation here.

1:15:40.208 --> 1:15:41.625
There's data on my cell phone
that can't be retrieved now,

1:15:41.708 --> 1:15:43.041
but I'd like to recover the data.

1:15:49.833 --> 1:15:52.708
STUDY NOTES

1:15:59.875 --> 1:16:02.458
Do you happen to know anyone that

1:16:02.541 --> 1:16:04.708
can fix cell phones and smartwatches?

1:16:04.791 --> 1:16:05.958
What?

1:16:06.041 --> 1:16:07.125
He changed jobs?

1:16:07.208 --> 1:16:09.458
The sun is setting.

1:16:10.541 --> 1:16:12.583
It's the old man's last day
before cremation.

1:16:13.458 --> 1:16:16.041
Has everyone done their part?

1:16:17.458 --> 1:16:19.750
Has the filial son been keeping vigil?

1:16:20.750 --> 1:16:23.083
Why am I the only one chanting here?

1:16:24.041 --> 1:16:26.333
How about we all make some noise?

1:16:28.916 --> 1:16:29.833
<i>Hey.</i>

1:16:29.916 --> 1:16:31.041
<i>It's me,</i>

1:16:32.125 --> 1:16:32.958
San.

1:16:35.625 --> 1:16:36.708
So it can't be done?

1:16:38.125 --> 1:16:39.750
JUNE 12TH, 2021

1:16:39.833 --> 1:16:41.250
<i>Look at this scrawl.</i>

1:16:41.333 --> 1:16:43.541
It's like a dung beetle
did it by crawling.

1:16:43.625 --> 1:16:45.791
CUSTOMIZATION, EXCLUSIVE FUNERAL

