BOSHI TECHNOLOGY

1:17:00.791 --> 1:17:02.375
If these guys can't do it,

1:17:02.458 --> 1:17:03.833
then no one else can.

1:17:03.916 --> 1:17:05.583
Everyone, please.
I'd really appreciate it.

1:17:15.833 --> 1:17:17.041
Well done.

