1:18:19.000 --> 1:18:20.500
It has ears

1:18:20.583 --> 1:18:22.250
and eyes now.

1:18:22.750 --> 1:18:24.583
The tail is different too.

1:18:25.166 --> 1:18:26.125
Give it a squeeze.

1:18:29.375 --> 1:18:30.916
<i>I made you lotus roots with pork ribs.</i>

1:18:31.000 --> 1:18:32.416
<i>It's ready to eat, Xiaowen.</i>

1:18:32.500 --> 1:18:34.250
<i>Where have you gone?</i>

1:18:35.250 --> 1:18:36.791
<i>Come home soon.</i>

1:18:36.875 --> 1:18:38.416
<i>Be careful on the way.</i>

1:18:39.916 --> 1:18:42.458
<i>Remember to drink a lot of water
when playing outside.</i>

1:18:42.541 --> 1:18:44.375
<i>Stand in the shade while you play.</i>

1:18:44.458 --> 1:18:46.708
<i>A girl won't look pretty</i>

1:18:46.791 --> 1:18:48.000
<i>with tanned skin.</i>

1:18:49.916 --> 1:18:53.625
<i>Baby, I got you a watermelon.
Come back and eat it.</i>

1:18:55.208 --> 1:18:56.875
<i>Our Xiaowen is the prettiest.</i>

1:18:56.958 --> 1:18:59.625
<i>Our Xiaowen is the best.</i>

1:19:00.125 --> 1:19:02.083
<i>Let's come home together.</i>

1:19:02.166 --> 1:19:05.458
<i>We'll get your favorite
gluttonous rice cake in brown sugar.</i>

1:19:07.458 --> 1:19:09.583
<i>Xiaowen, it's your birthday today.</i>

1:19:09.666 --> 1:19:12.166
<i>Don't spend too long playing outside.</i>

1:19:13.916 --> 1:19:15.208
<i>I bought you a new dress.</i>

1:19:15.291 --> 1:19:18.458
<i>Come back and try it on. See if it fits.</i>

1:19:19.833 --> 1:19:22.250
<i>Xiaowen, lock the door from the inside</i>

1:19:22.333 --> 1:19:25.625
<i>and don't open it no matter what.</i>

1:19:27.500 --> 1:19:30.291
<i>My big baby, please be patient.</i>

1:19:30.375 --> 1:19:32.166
<i>I'll be home soon.</i>

1:19:34.000 --> 1:19:35.291
<i>Grandma</i>

1:19:35.375 --> 1:19:37.666
<i>is great at making braids.</i>

1:19:37.750 --> 1:19:40.458
<i>I'll make the prettiest braid
for you tomorrow.</i>

1:19:40.541 --> 1:19:43.125
<i>My granddaughter
is the prettiest of them all.</i>

1:19:48.625 --> 1:19:51.458
-Take another bite.
-Good morning.

1:19:51.541 --> 1:19:53.083
Xiaowen, wait.

1:19:53.166 --> 1:19:54.958
-One moment.
-Your water bottle.

1:19:55.500 --> 1:19:56.833
-Good morning.
-Good morning.

1:19:56.916 --> 1:19:58.458
Don't forget to drink water.

1:20:05.583 --> 1:20:06.958
How come you're here?

1:20:07.041 --> 1:20:09.750
This is my little sister, Haifei.

1:20:09.833 --> 1:20:11.958
She is Xiaowen's biological mom.

1:20:14.166 --> 1:20:15.166
Over here.

1:20:17.000 --> 1:20:18.958
Didn't you tell me that her mom is dead?

1:20:19.541 --> 1:20:21.375
So the death certificate
you showed me was fake?

1:20:22.041 --> 1:20:22.875
I…

1:20:22.958 --> 1:20:24.541
The certificate is real.

1:20:24.625 --> 1:20:26.750
This is a very complicated situation.

1:20:26.833 --> 1:20:28.041
It's like this…

1:20:29.375 --> 1:20:30.916
Tell him yourself.

1:20:31.000 --> 1:20:32.208
I'm done.

1:20:34.750 --> 1:20:36.208
He's not lying, San.

1:20:38.250 --> 1:20:39.791
Where did you come from?

1:20:40.791 --> 1:20:42.458
Why should I just believe
everything you said

1:20:42.541 --> 1:20:43.833
and do whatever you asked me to?

1:20:46.666 --> 1:20:47.791
Xiaowen

1:20:47.875 --> 1:20:51.083
was born at 9 a.m. on July 6th, 2015.

1:20:51.166 --> 1:20:53.416
The whole birthing process took 27 hours.

1:20:53.500 --> 1:20:56.541
She wouldn't come out no matter what,
so I had to have a C-section in the end.

1:20:56.625 --> 1:20:58.666
There's a diamond-shaped birthmark
on her left foot.

1:20:58.750 --> 1:21:01.333
If you still don't believe me,
we can do a DNA test.

1:21:02.791 --> 1:21:04.708
I'm not letting you do any silly tests.

1:21:15.500 --> 1:21:16.500
Xiaowen.

1:21:18.625 --> 1:21:20.125
Have you ever met your mom?

1:21:20.208 --> 1:21:22.541
I have no mom or dad.

1:21:22.625 --> 1:21:24.208
I jumped out of a crack

1:21:24.291 --> 1:21:25.625
in a stone.

1:22:28.750 --> 1:22:29.708
Sir.

1:22:30.791 --> 1:22:34.500
I've been waiting out here all these days.

1:22:35.375 --> 1:22:37.541
It seems none of us can sleep--

1:22:37.625 --> 1:22:39.250
Where the hell have you been?

1:22:45.750 --> 1:22:47.458
Where were you when her grandma died?

1:22:48.208 --> 1:22:50.708
Where were you when she was
causing trouble all over the place?

1:22:51.333 --> 1:22:53.583
Where were you when her aunt
kicked her out of the house?

1:22:54.416 --> 1:22:56.583
Finally, she has a place
she could call home

1:22:56.666 --> 1:22:58.333
and you're trying to take her away?

1:22:59.416 --> 1:23:01.000
Who gave you the right?

1:23:01.958 --> 1:23:04.291
You're right. I deserve so much blame.

1:23:09.083 --> 1:23:10.083
Are you out of your mind?

1:23:10.583 --> 1:23:12.625
I left home when I was a teenager.

1:23:12.708 --> 1:23:15.083
I followed some classmates
and stepped straight into society.

1:23:15.166 --> 1:23:17.458
I didn't achieve anything
and gave birth to a child.

1:23:17.541 --> 1:23:19.416
My boyfriend ran away
when he saw I was pregnant.

1:23:20.291 --> 1:23:22.166
I refused to give up my dreams,
so I went abroad.

1:23:22.250 --> 1:23:24.125
I did something bad
and ended up in prison.

1:23:24.208 --> 1:23:26.750
My mom couldn't contact me,
so I was presumed dead.

1:23:27.791 --> 1:23:29.541
But even in prison,

1:23:29.625 --> 1:23:31.625
I thought about Xiaowen every day.

1:23:33.000 --> 1:23:34.708
I know I'm a bad mom.

1:23:34.791 --> 1:23:36.208
I've been a terrible mom,

1:23:36.291 --> 1:23:37.416
but…

1:23:38.958 --> 1:23:40.416
But she's still my child.

1:23:42.208 --> 1:23:43.500
I…

1:23:43.583 --> 1:23:45.333
And I'm still her mom.

1:23:46.208 --> 1:23:48.208
She came out of me.

1:23:57.791 --> 1:24:00.458
This is not a decision
I can make it by myself.

1:24:02.166 --> 1:24:05.000
There's also my buddy,
Jianren, and Baixue.

1:24:05.083 --> 1:24:07.000
I can't make their decisions for them.

1:24:08.250 --> 1:24:11.541
Sir.

1:24:12.708 --> 1:24:13.750
Please.

1:24:14.708 --> 1:24:15.916
I beg you.

1:24:16.875 --> 1:24:18.458
Give her back to me.

1:24:25.666 --> 1:24:26.750
Please, I'm begging you.

1:24:36.000 --> 1:24:36.916
How about

1:24:37.666 --> 1:24:40.083
you give me three more days?

1:24:42.083 --> 1:24:43.291
HEARSE FOR RENT

1:24:44.666 --> 1:24:45.833
Look at you, San.

1:24:45.916 --> 1:24:47.791
Now that's a rare sight to behold.

1:24:48.916 --> 1:24:51.083
I learned it from the Internet.

1:24:51.166 --> 1:24:52.416
Try it. I hope it's not too bad.

1:24:59.541 --> 1:25:01.916
Why do you look unhappy?

1:25:03.166 --> 1:25:04.000
What?

1:25:06.333 --> 1:25:07.375
No.

1:25:07.458 --> 1:25:08.791
I don't look unhappy.

1:25:09.375 --> 1:25:11.625
Do you have a hole in your jaw
where food leaks out?

1:25:19.541 --> 1:25:21.041
Your grandma was right.

1:25:21.708 --> 1:25:23.208
Every grain is the fruit of hard work.

1:25:24.916 --> 1:25:27.916
My teacher says there's another
parent-child class tomorrow.

1:25:28.000 --> 1:25:29.666
A parent needs to be present.

1:25:29.750 --> 1:25:31.250
Which one of you wants to go?

1:25:31.333 --> 1:25:32.625
-I do.
-I do.

1:25:32.708 --> 1:25:34.166
Only one though.

1:25:42.791 --> 1:25:43.833
I'll go.

1:25:46.000 --> 1:25:47.750
HUAJIAJIA KINDERGARTEN

1:25:47.833 --> 1:25:50.583
-Go!
-Go!

1:25:51.166 --> 1:25:52.791
-Go!
-Go!

1:26:19.166 --> 1:26:23.458
-Mom, Dad, thank you for everything.
-Dad, thank you for everything.

1:26:25.750 --> 1:26:27.291
I know

1:26:27.375 --> 1:26:29.166
that you've been lying to me.

1:26:29.708 --> 1:26:32.291
I'll never see my grandma again.

1:26:33.458 --> 1:26:34.625
But

1:26:35.291 --> 1:26:37.041
I'm not afraid anymore

1:26:38.416 --> 1:26:39.625
because

1:26:40.666 --> 1:26:43.125
I have a dad now.

1:27:27.125 --> 1:27:28.500
What is your dad's name?

1:27:28.583 --> 1:27:30.291
Mo Sanmei.

1:27:32.083 --> 1:27:33.250
Where does he live?

1:27:33.333 --> 1:27:35.875
Up Sky, No. 73, Huai'an Road,

1:27:35.958 --> 1:27:37.500
Yuhua District, Yanjiang City.

1:27:38.958 --> 1:27:40.458
What is your dad's cell phone number?

1:27:42.291 --> 1:27:44.625
What are you doing so late at night?

1:27:45.833 --> 1:27:47.750
I'm so sleepy.

1:27:53.625 --> 1:27:54.791
You won't

1:27:57.750 --> 1:27:59.375
forget about me in the future?

1:28:07.541 --> 1:28:09.083
I'll find a small mirror for you.

1:28:47.166 --> 1:28:49.416
UP SKY

1:29:19.333 --> 1:29:21.583
These are things that she'd use regularly.

1:29:22.250 --> 1:29:24.500
-Her clothes, her favorite snacks,
-Okay.

1:29:24.583 --> 1:29:25.583
and her school backpack.

1:29:26.250 --> 1:29:27.541
She doesn't like drinking water,

1:29:27.625 --> 1:29:29.333
so you have to make sure
she drinks plenty.

1:29:31.875 --> 1:29:33.500
This cloth tiger is called Beans.

1:29:33.583 --> 1:29:36.416
Her grandma sewed it for her.
It's her favorite thing in the world.

1:29:36.500 --> 1:29:39.041
She likes grabbing the arm
of an adult when she sleeps.

1:29:39.125 --> 1:29:40.958
She likes putting her mouth here.

1:29:41.750 --> 1:29:43.583
She eats too fast.

1:29:43.666 --> 1:29:45.000
Also, you have to remind her that

1:29:45.083 --> 1:29:46.625
food on the ground shouldn't be eaten.

1:29:46.708 --> 1:29:48.125
I'm warning you.

1:29:49.000 --> 1:29:50.833
You have to be good to her.

1:29:50.916 --> 1:29:53.416
I've been to prison,
so I don't mind going back again.

1:30:05.500 --> 1:30:07.708
Here's some money.
It's not much, but you should take it.

1:30:07.791 --> 1:30:09.250
-I can't take this.
-Take it.

1:30:09.333 --> 1:30:11.166
-I can't take this.
-Take it! It's not for you.

1:30:11.250 --> 1:30:13.125
-It's for Xiaowen.
-San?

1:30:13.666 --> 1:30:14.875
Where is this?

1:30:16.291 --> 1:30:17.708
Who are you?

1:30:19.208 --> 1:30:22.625
Child, I am your mom.

1:30:22.708 --> 1:30:24.291
-I'm taking you home.
-I don't have a mom.

1:30:24.875 --> 1:30:26.333
-How can that be?
-Xiaowen.

1:30:26.416 --> 1:30:27.791
Xiaowen, listen to me.

1:30:27.875 --> 1:30:29.416
She really is your mom

1:30:29.500 --> 1:30:30.750
and she has come to take you home.

1:30:30.833 --> 1:30:33.541
-I'm not going with her. Let me go!
-Xiaowen.

1:30:33.625 --> 1:30:34.625
Let go!

1:30:34.708 --> 1:30:35.916
-I'm not going with her!
-Be good.

1:30:36.000 --> 1:30:38.083
-Be good.
-I have no mom. I'm not going with her!

1:30:38.166 --> 1:30:40.333
Please let us go.

1:30:40.416 --> 1:30:41.250
Just let us go.

1:30:41.333 --> 1:30:43.833
I'm not going with her! Let me go!

1:30:43.916 --> 1:30:47.000
-Go. Drive!
-I'm not going with her! Let me go!

1:30:47.083 --> 1:30:48.000
San!

1:30:48.083 --> 1:30:49.666
Back here.

1:30:50.625 --> 1:30:52.625
San!

1:30:53.500 --> 1:30:54.833
-I'm not going with her!
-Be good.

1:30:54.916 --> 1:30:56.666
-Be good and come home with me.
-San!

1:31:01.333 --> 1:31:03.083
San!

1:31:07.375 --> 1:31:08.500
<i>Stop shouting, Xiaowen.</i>

1:31:08.583 --> 1:31:10.000
-San!
-Xiaowen.

1:31:10.666 --> 1:31:12.125
-San!
-Back here.

1:31:16.916 --> 1:31:18.500
Stop hitting and screaming.

1:31:18.583 --> 1:31:21.000
Dad!

1:31:22.041 --> 1:31:24.041
Dad!

1:32:15.875 --> 1:32:18.791
UP SKY

1:32:23.833 --> 1:32:26.083
You're always so full of yourself.

1:32:27.250 --> 1:32:28.708
Did you ask Xiaowen what she wanted?

1:32:31.375 --> 1:32:32.916
Did you ask us what we wanted?

1:32:34.166 --> 1:32:36.166
Technically, we're her parents!

1:32:37.791 --> 1:32:39.625
She's registered under my household.

1:32:40.625 --> 1:32:42.458
You're so selfish.

1:32:43.708 --> 1:32:45.583
You're so selfish.

1:32:46.416 --> 1:32:47.666
You're so selfish.

1:32:49.916 --> 1:32:51.958
You want to give up the business? Fine!

1:32:52.041 --> 1:32:53.375
Let's do it now!

1:32:53.458 --> 1:32:54.458
Pack our things.

1:32:54.541 --> 1:32:56.125
You are a heartless beast.

1:32:56.833 --> 1:32:58.291
No wonder your dad looks down on you!

1:32:58.916 --> 1:33:00.958
No wonder your girlfriend cheated on you!

1:33:05.875 --> 1:33:07.375
You don't deserve to be called human!

1:33:07.458 --> 1:33:08.583
Bastard.

1:33:18.083 --> 1:33:19.083
<i>Sanmei,</i>

1:33:20.041 --> 1:33:22.041
<i>Dad is gone.</i>

1:33:55.333 --> 1:33:56.291
<i>My children,</i>

1:33:57.250 --> 1:33:59.625
<i>sooner or later, this day would come,</i>

1:34:01.250 --> 1:34:04.083
<i>so I've prepared a letter for you two.</i>

1:34:06.208 --> 1:34:08.875
<i>You shouldn't feel sad about my passing.</i>

1:34:09.666 --> 1:34:13.166
<i>Everyone has to face this inevitability.</i>

1:34:16.375 --> 1:34:17.375
<i>San,</i>

1:34:17.458 --> 1:34:20.041
<i>I'll leave
the funeral arrangements to you.</i>

1:34:21.000 --> 1:34:24.375
<i>Don't give me that big ceremony crap.</i>

1:34:24.458 --> 1:34:26.375
<i>I've seen enough of that in my lifetime.</i>

1:34:28.541 --> 1:34:31.541
<i>I want to leave this world clean and pure.</i>

1:34:31.625 --> 1:34:33.958
<i>Just like how I came into this world.</i>

1:34:35.291 --> 1:34:36.833
<i>Keep the spending low</i>

1:34:37.916 --> 1:34:38.791
<i>and remember this.</i>

1:34:39.583 --> 1:34:41.458
<i>I'm watching you.</i>

1:35:12.500 --> 1:35:15.791
<i>I'd like a customized funeral</i>

1:35:15.875 --> 1:35:18.000
<i>that's both dignified and inexpensive.</i>

1:35:19.833 --> 1:35:22.125
<i>Instead of splashing
on a ceremonial casket,</i>

1:35:22.208 --> 1:35:25.833
<i>I'd rather you spend
the money on a family feast.</i>

1:35:25.916 --> 1:35:27.833
<i>After the cremation,</i>

1:35:27.916 --> 1:35:31.041
<i>put me in that can.</i>

1:35:32.750 --> 1:35:34.708
<i>And the dispatching of my remains,</i>

1:35:34.791 --> 1:35:36.583
<i>I'll leave that to you.</i>

1:35:36.666 --> 1:35:40.500
<i>Think of this as a test from your dad.</i>

1:35:42.500 --> 1:35:45.000
<i>If you can't think of an answer,</i>

1:35:45.083 --> 1:35:47.500
<i>I'll just stay in the can</i>

1:35:47.583 --> 1:35:48.666
<i>and going nowhere.</i>

1:36:10.291 --> 1:36:12.208
My sister, how should we do this?

1:36:12.750 --> 1:36:13.791
How should we do what?

1:36:15.125 --> 1:36:17.458
How do we dispatch Dad's remains?

1:36:17.541 --> 1:36:19.458
Buried together with mom's, of course.

1:36:20.125 --> 1:36:23.166
No, Dad was very clear in his will.

1:36:23.250 --> 1:36:25.625
He said he wants a special funeral
that's different.

1:36:25.708 --> 1:36:27.291
Well, how special can a funeral be?

1:36:27.375 --> 1:36:29.125
Where else can we put it
if not underground?

1:36:29.208 --> 1:36:30.500
In the sky?

1:36:36.541 --> 1:36:37.500
Sanmei!

1:36:37.583 --> 1:36:38.750
Stop!

1:36:39.833 --> 1:36:41.125
Stop him!

1:36:41.208 --> 1:36:42.250
-Go after him.
-Leave now!

1:36:42.333 --> 1:36:43.291
Quick.

1:36:43.375 --> 1:36:44.833
-In the car. Quick.
-Okay.

1:36:48.125 --> 1:36:49.250
QINGTIAN FUNERAL PARLOR

1:36:49.333 --> 1:36:50.541
Faster.

1:36:54.750 --> 1:36:57.041
San, I can't believe
you left me out of something this big.

1:36:57.125 --> 1:36:59.708
-Do you not think of me as your friend?
-Well, here I am, aren't I?

1:36:59.791 --> 1:37:00.708
-Quick.
-Go.

1:37:02.208 --> 1:37:03.208
UP SKY

1:37:06.625 --> 1:37:08.416
Sanmei, stop.

1:37:09.000 --> 1:37:10.458
Stop now!

1:37:16.458 --> 1:37:17.458
San.

1:37:31.375 --> 1:37:34.000
-Hurry up.
-Quick.

1:37:35.083 --> 1:37:36.375
Hold my sister up!

1:37:38.041 --> 1:37:39.000
Sanmei.

1:37:39.083 --> 1:37:40.333
Stop!

1:37:40.416 --> 1:37:41.500
-Ma'am.
-Stop right there.

1:37:41.583 --> 1:37:42.750
-Don't come closer.
-Stop.

1:37:42.833 --> 1:37:43.708
Take this.

1:37:43.791 --> 1:37:45.291
-Sanmei.
-Don't go.

1:37:45.375 --> 1:37:46.208
-All right.
-Quick.

1:37:46.291 --> 1:37:47.125
Stay back.

1:37:47.208 --> 1:37:48.958
Here, it's dangerous over there.

1:38:55.416 --> 1:38:56.291
Dad,

1:38:59.875 --> 1:39:01.500
how is this for dignified?

1:39:39.333 --> 1:39:40.416
Xiaowen is missing.

1:39:51.125 --> 1:39:52.791
I have a dream.

1:39:52.875 --> 1:39:54.875
I want to be an…

1:39:54.958 --> 1:39:56.041
Is she with you?

1:39:56.125 --> 1:39:57.208
Xiaowen!

1:40:30.666 --> 1:40:32.458
CUSTOMIZATION, EXCLUSIVE FUNERAL

1:40:35.958 --> 1:40:38.166
UP SKY

1:40:38.250 --> 1:40:39.666
San!

1:40:52.166 --> 1:40:53.208
Where have you been?

1:40:53.291 --> 1:40:54.333
Tell me. Where were you?

1:40:54.416 --> 1:40:55.958
Why are you running around
in the middle of the night?

1:40:56.041 --> 1:40:57.541
What if you're kidnapped by bad guys?

1:40:57.625 --> 1:40:58.750
What if you got lost?

1:41:03.500 --> 1:41:06.583
My dad's name is Mo Sanmei.

1:41:07.625 --> 1:41:12.375
My home is Up Sky, No. 73, Huai'an Road,

1:41:12.458 --> 1:41:15.000
Yuhua District, Yanjiang City.

1:41:16.250 --> 1:41:17.916
I won't get lost.

